<p class="ql-align-center">如果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“美丽长乐"大行动</strong>是一幅画卷</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从整洁长乐到绿色长乐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再到人文长乐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最绚丽的篇章便是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人文长乐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/6a59e905ac3e462186492f094cce8c51.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">近年来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">鹤上镇依托<strong>“美丽长乐”大行动</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不断推进人文长乐建设</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在展现高雅文林、培育人才的基础上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">描绘出一幅幅层林尽染的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人文景致</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/87b7891f790f454f9157081425029e98.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
