<p class="ql-align-center">走进鹤上镇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅拥有便利的交通、整洁的环境</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还保留着绿水青山的秀气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坐拥田园风光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">和悠悠人文古韵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">交相辉映</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让人好不向往</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200904/e3a0f8ffc68f413eaf104f2911776ddd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>九头马古民居</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>灰墙黛瓦</strong>的九头马古民居群落</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保存完好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以淡墨似的写意</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">横卧于鹤上镇岐阳村的天马山之麓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/971994fb9aaa481ca6481e0c8e9eb269.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">九头马古民居</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是福建省面积最大的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古民居建筑之一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">乃福州地区晚清建筑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">独具匠心的代表作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/f7856f397ed14002bf742dd9d9e058ed.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它所散发出的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古典神韵与文化张力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不仅体现在建筑上的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">恢宏与精美</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且在布局和陈设上</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也深具民居生活的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">特色与魅力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/b72f8b16642a4fb3b7df5f66a0c0901a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/efc2d011fac34fa590a849c1150a80d8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给人一种宁静与平和</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">恢宏和淳朴之感</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">散发出</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">悠悠的古老芬芳</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/8d1c4520b1334e9b81d841a07651ff81.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200904/8032408e7dc2469b999a33cf017c7d52.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流连于宏大的二十五落厅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古民居深宅大院</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">瞬间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历史气息扑面而来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人文 <strong>李骐祠</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">明成祖永乐年间状元<strong>李骐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自幼聪慧异常</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">十岁即能通读《孝经》《论语》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200904/0645e27de77448a8a49163fb91585f4d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李骐祠建于明初</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">坐落在鹤上镇沙京上李村</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面朝沙京街，背靠莲花山</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"> 经过修缮和保护</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">依然焕发着勃勃生机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">祠内绿植郁郁葱葱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更添几分雅致</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200904/7c006b1dfe094dc3a5d3148f6afe925e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">祠内匾额对联</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">文字佳妙、意义深远</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其中最引人注目的便是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“秦河怀厚德，翰苑仰芳名”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正是李骐家世和仕途的真实写照</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>陈振龙纪念馆 </strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“番薯之父”<strong>陈振龙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从吕宋引入番薯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">解决了无数人的温饱</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让他们得以在饥荒中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">存活下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">郭沫若颂其功绩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>“当得比神农”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/d2f285d1a14c4dc5833b22e2f4a9a193.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/723d63ecd0af4b4f9e065c285f974a98.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">陈振龙纪念亭恢弘大气</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">故居内各式展品</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都还在诉说着这段千古传奇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">记载着陈振龙一家七代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">引种、推广番薯的历史功绩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>李兆珍纪念堂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">历经沧桑的<strong>李兆珍纪念堂</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">经过维护、检修</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不断强化日常管理</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">消除各类安全隐患</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保存较完整</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">廊檐雕刻余韵仍存</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200904/c821a7c89f5040fd9ff498f51d17cbdc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>李兆珍</strong>(1846-1927年)，学名邴，字星冶，清道光二十六年生，同治十二年(1873年)举人，清王朝天津、开封知府。辛亥革命后，历任参议院参议、安徽巡按使、国会议员、安徽省长等职。他热爱家乡，数度出资兴建乡学，修葺状元李骐特祠与龙泉古刹。民国八年七月大潮，北乡百余村遭海啸席卷，他毅然在天津街头卖字筹款，汇回银元二万三千元赈灾。他还是书法名家，造诣精深。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>李兆珍书法作品</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/26d44425a2ac49159c1684fa57db8b48.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200904/26cb5ffc93c841429317f16ce16d2821.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200904/804f87f7d24543f9ac767709b3382075.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">徜徉在鹤上镇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">古厝的风情中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看着直指苍穹的飞檐翘角</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那些技艺精湛的雕梁画栋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">清新淡雅的灰墙黛瓦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/4c72c4e054404040ac485fcd9c6980a7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不禁感叹鹤上镇</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">落实<strong>“美丽长乐”大行动</strong>的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">累累硕果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">美丽乡村建设</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是“一阵子”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也不是一代人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不是一个模板</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或者一个面孔</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更不是一成不变</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/331db194c7b743928d095cc878543e07.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因地制宜</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">挖掘人文历史</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在寻根溯源中，弘扬传统美德</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是<strong>美丽乡村建设</strong>中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不可或缺的一部分</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200904/e2adc40a9e0b4404bfde5b6a4a025a74.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">愿更多人感受到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">人文的魅力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">保护<strong>历史文脉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让这样的宝贵文化</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>代代相传</strong>......</p>
